Apistogramma viejita... A wide variety of aquatic plants, as well as driftwoods of different postures and strange - looking landscaping stones, are waiting for you to arrange.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472890/extras/f9aee4fdb8408b38549357742fef2e79.poster.avif?t=1774512602\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472890/extras/f9aee4fdb8408b38549357742fef2e79.webm?t=1774512602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472890/extras/f9aee4fdb8408b38549357742fef2e79.mp4?t=1774512602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472890/extras/2e5e0e64babdc43e7fc2e3b4ca05a52c.poster.avif?t=1774512602\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472890/extras/2e5e0e64babdc43e7fc2e3b4ca05a52c.webm?t=1774512602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472890/extras/2e5e0e64babdc43e7fc2e3b4ca05a52c.mp4?t=1774512602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
